727459f-a.title: Queens: National Street - 42nd Street
727459f-a.text:
National Street, at the N.W. corner of 42nd Street,
showing the Union Evangelical Church. It was built in
1871. Charles P. Leverich donated the site and edifice
providing that it remain forever undenominational and free.
View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection April,1925
MAY BE REPRODUCED
Views 2,3: P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS  October 2, 1935
